---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';

const posts = await getCollection('posts');
// Sort by publish date, newest first
posts.sort((a, b) => b.data.pubDate.getTime() - a.data.pubDate.getTime());
---

<Layout title="Sätteri Mermaid 测试博客" description="展示 @xingwangzhe/satteri-mermaid 的各种 Mermaid 图表渲染效果">
	<h2 style="border-bottom: none; margin-top: 0;">📝 文章列表</h2>
	<ul class="post-list">
		{posts.map(post => (
			<li class="post-item">
				<h2><a href={`/posts/${post.id}/`}>{post.data.title}</a></h2>
				<p class="post-date">
					{new Date(post.data.pubDate).toLocaleDateString('zh-CN', {
						year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric',
					})}
				</p>
				<p class="post-desc">{post.data.description}</p>
				{post.data.tags.length > 0 && (
					<div class="tags">
						{post.data.tags.map(tag => <span class="tag">{tag}</span>)}
					</div>
				)}
			</li>
		))}
	</ul>

	<hr />

	<section>
		<h2>🎨 实时预览：Mermaid 流程图</h2>
		<p>下面是一个直接在页面 Markdown 中渲染的 Mermaid 流程图：</p>

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Sätteri] -->|MDAST Plugin| B[检测代码块]
    B --> C[mermaid-rs 渲染]
    C --> D[静态 SVG]
    D --> E[零 JS 输出]
    E -->|HAST Plugin| F[最终 HTML]
```

		<p>✨ 上图在 <code>astro build</code> 时已渲染为静态内联 SVG，无需任何客户端 JavaScript。</p>
	</section>
</Layout>
